/blockquote><br />\n點文青法</blockquote><br />\n最起碼要鐘意睇書睇戲，文哲史最少都要知下<br />\n睇既野全面同廣d，起碼諗法行為都唔會隨波逐流同短視<br />\n識自己思考，做事有自己信念或者原則<br />\n<br />\n由知性締造既獨特性？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔太識點形容</blockquote><br />\n現實係鬼有男仔欣賞呢啲女仔咩<br />\n我夠鍾意睇書睇戲 但無人欣賞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n樣既問題，sorry</blockquote><br />\n樣係基本野<br />\n其他只係合格之後加幾多分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee35df1ce76821084d3d6e8b4d278a58b439e604","tid":116780,"uid":34503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T04:14:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>真文青女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點文青法</blockquote><br />\n最起碼要鐘意睇書睇戲，文哲史最少都要知下<br />\n睇既野全面同廣d，起碼諗法行為都唔會隨波逐流同短視<br />\n識自己思考，做事有自己信念或者原則<br />\n<br />\n由知性締造既獨特性？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔太識點形容</blockquote><br />\n現實係鬼有男仔欣賞呢啲女仔咩<br />\n我夠鍾意睇書睇戲 但無人欣賞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n樣既問題，sorry</blockquote><br />\n咩書咩戲先<br />\n識個真文青<br />\n真係同佢傾乜都傾到喎<br />\n即使佢唔靚仲要成面粒粒<br />\n我都覺得佢好有魅力"},{"pid":"1a3f1aff378c3acbee2f148fc1102896a0667141","tid":116780,"uid":3599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T04:27:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>真文青女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點文青法</blockquote><br />\n最起碼要鐘意睇書睇戲，文哲史最少都要知下<br />\n睇既野全面同廣d，起碼諗法行為都唔會隨波逐流同短視<br />\n識自己思考，做事有自己信念或者原則<br />\n<br />\n由知性締造既獨特性？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔太識點形容</blockquote><br />\n現實係鬼有男仔欣賞呢啲女仔咩<br />\n我夠鍾意睇書睇戲 但無人欣賞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n樣既問題，sorry</blockquote><br />\n咩書咩戲先<br />\n識個真文青<br />\n真係同佢傾乜都傾到喎<br />\n即使佢唔靚仲要成面粒粒<br />\n我都覺得佢好有魅力</blockquote><br />\n通常日本文學 說不上係甚麼文青<br />\n只不過都有掂下<br />\n睇開村上春樹東野圭吾太宰治個啲<br />\n電影就通常睇舊戲 同埋外國啲片<br />\n最近睇過呢幾套<br />\nBlack swan,the dead poets society,Flight club ,Pulp fiction<br />\n自問都叫乜嘢都有掂下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我個樣絕對唔係嗰種討好嘅樣<br />\n可能因為我個樣好惡 成日黑面<br />\n同埋冇乜氣質吸引人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n只不過有時候見到就算有啲人個樣麻麻都有男女朋友<br />\n就覺得點解人有我無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"504432ae421e3b6b3e3f525f17b49f24ac4bb03d","tid":116780,"uid":36788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T04:30:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>大波淫底嗰個</blockquote><br />\n唔使淫底，大波就得</blockquote><br />\n大波死魚 微波淫底<br />\n點揀</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n微波死魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da2373de8e7b20f8ffa46cb117ac6f4847cb332a","tid":116780,"uid":27274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T04:36:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>靚就得</blockquote><br />\n一睇就知你廿歲都未夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真男人唔係睇條女靚唔靚，仲要睇身材<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 兩樣嘢都有就話之佢文青定sporty啦</blockquote><br />\n自以為好醒既老屎忽係到講埋晒啲廢話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"637cae40e7c2d6291b7c5168847d2827e27c01df","tid":116780,"uid":33336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T04:42:19.000Z","msg":"運動文青型"}]}